description:
"Uncharted Territory" is a CTM style custom map, created by AMLP. The goal is to find all 16 different colored wool along with an iron, gold, and diamond block, and place 1 of each on a special victory monument. 

Survival skills are vital because the wool is in dangerous dungeons, resources are scarce, and traps are everywhere.

Map Name: Uncharted Territory
Map By: AnotherMinecraftLP (AMLP)
Map Thread: http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1380417-ctm-collection-amlps-uncharted-territory-series-132-3000-downloads/
